{"tid":2297214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有魚蛋革命義士判監36個月","createTime":"2020-11-23T06:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T10:05:52.000Z","uid":238696,"like":38,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"0992dda562783e570a8b3a789ab4d627754c356e","tid":2297214,"uid":238696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"旺暴案3男分別涉暴動刑毀縱火4罪　被囚27至36個月<br />\n11月23日(一) 13:42<br />\n<br />\n旺角暴亂事件發生距今4年，3名男子分別被控暴動、縱火和刑事損毀等共4罪，其中首被告譚百熙及第三被告王國斌早前分別承認暴動及刑毀，兩人今天（23日）在區域法院分別被判入獄36個月及27個月；而經審訊後被裁定縱火罪成的次被告陳舜堯，則判監36個月。<br />\n<br />\n3名被告依次是22歲酒保譚百熙、32歲游泳教練陳舜堯和23歲學生王國斌。譚承認於2016年2月9日，在旺角豉油街與其他人參與暴動。王承認兩項刑毀罪，指他於同日在山東街與身份不詳人士，損壞屬於政府的標誌杆及行人路。陳則否認一項縱火罪，被指用火損壞屬於中國香港體操總會的一塊橫額，早前經審訊被裁定罪成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=6efb3584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>唔貼link，蘋果未出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32f93ba174c95c027d375fd851f8af6429ec7a3","tid":2297214,"uid":238696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39944b4889a15bb71306350e893dd2839c384313","tid":2297214,"uid":238696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8feec020a0342c8df5a9cd88f175eb318df34326","tid":2297214,"uid":238696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3302cc54daab699b4c859dab47a388fdbbe1861f","tid":2297214,"uid":120807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:27:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d55421e0da491b1b10a60ca0dcba50e31c9180b","tid":2297214,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply